# NOTE: widget/dist/ IS committed.
# Rationale: the `widget-bundle-size` Verification Oracle (Probe A + Probe B)
# scans built artifacts in widget/dist/*.{js,mjs,css} on every commit. Without
# tracked dist/, the oracle has nothing to verify in CI before npm install +
# build runs, which would defeat the inner-loop closure the oracle exists to
# provide. The dist/ files are minified output; reviewing diffs is intentional
# friction that surfaces accidental bundle-size growth.
